{
  "texts": [
    "Ease of access and barriers to use We supplemented each score with a concise rationale to justify the scoring criteria and provide references for key claims.",
    "We summed and averaged the element scores to give a total maturity and availability score out of five.",
    "The rest of the project team then reviewed and confirmed the scores and rationales.",
    "We also specified for each tool whether it has open-source code, weights or data.",
    "26 If all three are open-source, we describe the tool as 'fully open-source'."
  ]
}